<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛兰克和丽莎正在和爷爷一起享受着美味的冰淇淋蛋卷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冰淇淋好吃吗，爷爷？”丽莎问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好吃。”爷爷回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们吃完冰淇淋去看萤火虫怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛兰克和丽莎同意了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走到冰淇淋商店后面的树旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黄昏已经来临，到处都是萤火虫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！我抓到了一只萤火虫！”佛兰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么它会发光？”丽莎问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。爷爷，是什么让萤火虫发光的？”佛兰克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是个很好的问题，佛兰克。”爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“萤火虫的胃里有一种一碰到氧气就会发光的化学物质。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道只有雄性萤火虫才能发光吗？”爷爷问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不知道，为什么？”佛兰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雄性萤火虫为了吸引雌性萤火虫而发光。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它闪烁得越频繁，吸引到的雌性萤火虫就越多。”爷爷解释说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇，您很了解萤火虫啊！”丽莎说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>丽莎、佛兰克的父母和奶奶也加入了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我像你这么大的时候。”爷爷继续说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们经常用萤火虫点亮房间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？”丽莎和佛兰克喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“才不是呢。”妈妈说，“爷爷夸张了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“时候不早了。”奶奶说，“我们该走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的。”爷爷回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家坐在卡车后面，要记住：不要站起来或者把手伸到窗外。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷把他们安全地送到家里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们到家了。”爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奶奶和我有一份惊喜给你们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奶奶把他们带到卧室后，打开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里面有一个双层床。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们的爷爷为你们做了这个床。”奶奶说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太酷了。”佛兰克说，“我要睡在上层。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也想睡在上层。”丽莎抱怨道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很抱歉，丽莎。”爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是佛兰克年龄更大一点儿。他应该睡在上面。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“需要我帮你上去吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不用，不过你能把特里递给我吗？”佛兰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特里？”爷爷问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特里是佛兰克的雷克斯暴龙。”妈妈笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，特里长得很吓人，可以把怪兽吓跑。”佛兰克又说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他爬上了床。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我知道了。”爷爷把特里递给了佛兰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是房子里没有怪兽。我已经把它们吓跑了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的爷爷很会吓跑怪兽。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“晚安。我会把门开着，客厅的灯也不会关。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“晚安，妈妈。”佛兰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“晚安。”丽莎说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在深夜，佛兰克的恐龙掉了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，特里！你还好吗？”他小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特里，你还好吗？你吓着了吗？”丽莎说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛兰克爬下来找特里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特里和我能跟你和多莉一起睡吗？”佛兰克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特里害怕睡在上面。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。”丽莎带着睡意说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你要保证特里不会吃掉多莉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不会的。”佛兰克保证说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>早上，爷爷和妈妈进房间里叫醒孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“佛兰克、丽莎，该起床了。我们要去湖边。”爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的。”佛兰克和丽莎说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“佛兰克，为什么你和丽莎睡在一起？”妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特里从上铺掉下来了。”佛兰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>339374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我下来找特里，但是它太害怕，不想上去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>339375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以我们跟丽莎一起睡了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错。”丽莎回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“而且特里还保证说不会吃掉多莉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>350779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>